itedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T05:30:43.000Z","msg":"我2003-2006住坡<br />\n而家其實無唔比食 <br />\n只係全國人都知政府唔鐘意 無人敢入口入貨 <br />\n你帶過去食 集集聲都無人捉你的"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T05:32:24.000Z","msg":"會唔會好似中國咁<br />\n有1，2個突然唔見左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋唔係大學生係唔係好慘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T05:44:33.000Z","msg":"....你係咪傻撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔清楚，我果陣係13-16歲。未有社會觀念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果3年比我既感覺 除左好撚熱之外 <br />\n其實幾好住 食野好食過香港 仲要好平<br />\n<br />\n果陣香港茶記一個飯野飲好似30-35蚊<br />\n我係果面係4-5蚊坡紙食到 我去果陣係1兌4 姐係16-20蚊左右<br />\n<br />\n囡囡個個都好性感 講緊2003年已經係咁 而家可能淨係著泳衣出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好就係太細 你基本上係無野可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  日日做運動 放假都係做運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同煙好貴 聽聞而家14，15蚊坡紙一包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd73775bc3c5729216621dc6315bd5dc0e66e87","tid":742990,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T05:45:32.000Z","msg":"印度"},{"pid":"4a069c3d0344bd259d960aee54660530445269c2","tid":742990,"uid":69090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T05:45:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9f6d88e0dfbf48eddee7240b6752969ae57e9ae","tid":742990,"uid":181822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9cd73775bc3c5729216621dc6315bd5dc0e66e87","tid":742990,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T05:45:32.000Z","msg":"印度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T06:09:10.000Z","msg":"俾你去強姦人?<br />\n仲衰過強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12633473de24c10d8767ed2d006e5b72867a7642","tid":742990,"uid":194476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T07:16:3